              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Wait & Save: Get a Discount by Waiting More</strong><br/>
                Lead of a Company Star Product: 0 to 1, Expanding in 35+ Countries, Becoming the #1 Largest Product in the US After UberX.
              </div>
