          <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
              <span>Led the Competitive Strategy with a 9-Figure Quarterly Budget; Maintained #1 Market Share Despite Two Competitor Launches and a Top Competitor Acquisition/Relaunch.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
              <span>Led Pricing, Incentives, and Marketplace Efficiency in Multiple EU Markets, Including a Company Star Market.</span>
            </li>
