          <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
              <span>MEVP is the Largest Independent Venture Capital Firm in the MENA Region by AUM Size.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
