              <span>YouTube: Grew Three Channels to 180k+, 15k+, and 2k+ Subscribers (>40M Total Views). Managed a Team of 3 Scriptwriters and 3 Editors to Produce 4 Videos/Week.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
              <span>Life Coach: Built a Community of 500 Users with Coaching Calls and Digital Courses.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
